Week 1-2: Focus on setting up Node.js and understanding core modules, basic server, and file handling.
Week 3-4: Learn Express.js, routing, middleware, and build simple RESTful APIs.
Week 5: Explore working with databases (MongoDB or SQL).
Week 6: Add user authentication with JWT and handle authorization.
Week 7: Dive into more advanced topics like performance tuning, WebSockets, and scaling.


